content: Royole Technology, the originator of foldable screen mobile phones, has owed wages for a year, with a total amount of more than 40 million yuan. Employees went on strike to demand wages. On December 25, at the Royole International Display Base in Longgang District, Shenzhen, about 50 Royole Technology employees gathered at the door of the base to strike for rights and demanded that the company pay wages. According to a Royole employee at the scene, the company currently has only about 200-300 employees, most of whom are engineers who maintain production line equipment, and the business is only basic screen assembly business, "income is only enough to pay social security." Royole Technology is a fully flexible screen manufacturer. It claims that the innovative ultra-low temperature non-silicon process integration technology is the "domestic light" that breaks Samsung's monopoly.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
On December 25, the retrial of the "case of a family of 18 villagers who privately built a floating bridge and was sentenced" was pronounced. The Intermediate People's Court of Baicheng City, Jilin Province, publicly pronounced the retrial of the case of Huang Deyi and 18 others for provoking troubles, and upheld the conviction and sentencing of Huang Deyi and He Shuchun in accordance with the law. Huang Song, Huang Qiang, Huang Dejun, Huang Deyou, and Liu Yanhui were exempted from criminal punishment. Huang Yong, Huang Gang, Huang Wei, Liu Yanjie, He Shuyun, Zuo Qingzhi, Wu Fengqing, Long Li, Liu Haibo, Li Li, and Bian Guang were declared not guilty.
On December 31, 2019, the People's Court of Taonan City, Jilin Province sentenced Huang Deyi to two years in prison for the crime of provoking troubles, suspended for two years, and sentenced He Shuchun and 17 others to one year in prison, six months of detention, and three months of imprisonment, and announced suspended sentences at the same time.
The court found out after retrial that Huang Deyi and others illegally occupied the river without approval from the administrative authorities and built a bridge. In order to obtain illegal profits, they blocked and destroyed the access road and the old road in the river, causing some vehicles to fall into the pit and suffer property losses, making other vehicles unable or afraid to pass through the old road and forced to cross the river from the bridge involved in the case.
Huang Deyi and others set up iron chains and ropes at the bridge head and took shifts all day to intercept passing vehicles and forcibly collect bridge tolls, which caused disputes and disputes many times. Huang Deyi and others built the bridge privately and refused to correct it after multiple administrative penalties. They continued to implement the above behavior knowing that it was illegal, ignored national laws and regulations and administrative penalties, and forcibly took other people's property many times, which seriously disrupted the social management order. This behavior has constituted the crime of provoking trouble. Huang Deyi played a major role in the joint crime and was the principal offender. The original judgment sentenced him appropriately and should be upheld. He Shuchun participated deeply and played a greater role. The original judgment sentenced him appropriately and should be upheld.

According to a 2019 survey of 70,000 representative samples randomly drawn linearly by Beijing Normal University, about 5.46 million people in the country have zero monthly income; 220 million people have a monthly income of less than 500 yuan; 420 million people have a monthly income of less than 800 yuan; 550 million people have a monthly income of less than 1,000 yuan; and 600 million people have a monthly income of less than 1,090 yuan.
